pan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c14 c69"><span>1.</span><span class="c11">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="c1">El usuario ingresa a la pantalla de administraci&oacute;n de productos. All&iacute; puede:</span></p><p class="c14 c42"><span>a)</span><span class="c11">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Crear un producto:</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c1">1.El usuario ingresa los siguientes valores en un formulario en pantalla:</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Nombre de producto.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Descripci&oacute;n.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Precio de compra.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Precio de &uacute;ltima compra.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Costo est&aacute;ndar.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Precio de venta.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Moneda.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Marca.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Proveedores.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span class="c11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">Estado de producto.</span></p><p class="c14 c35"><span>&middot;</span><span cla